Class UnknownExperimentException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable

        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.optimizely.ab.OptimizelyRuntimeException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UnknownExperimentException
extends OptimizelyRuntimeException
    Exception thrown when attempting to use/refer to an Experiment that isn't present in the current ProjectConfig.

    This may occur if code changes are made prior to the experiment being setup in the Optimizely application.
